    "id": 1304949,
    "position": 3,
    "description": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_74070000000000001/attachments/8409020/dp_app.css\"><h4>Review the case and the three PowerPoint presentations.&nbsp; As you read over the materials, consider how O’Malley should structure his presentation at the partners’ meeting.&nbsp; The following are among the issues you may wish to consider:</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Which company should he recommend? Which uncertainties should he highlight?</li>\n<li>Are there valuation issues that he should point out?</li>\n<li>What organizational issues are likely to influence the partners’ decision</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>ASSIGNMENT: Choose one deal on Tad’s behalf and prepare a set of three PowerPoint slides that he should use when presenting to the general partners. Students will make a presentation in class. – BE PREPARED!</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>SUBMIT: Hard copy of the PPT slides at the beginning of class.</strong></p><script src=\"https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_74070000000000001/attachments/8409019/dp_app.js\"></script>",
